{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"586","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"報告：氣候政策趨嚴 若干產業價值恐大幅縮水","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>時間：<span lang='EN-US'>2019-12-09 14:43 </span>新聞引據：中央社撰稿編輯：海青青</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%83%B9%E5%80%BC.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 491px;' /></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>PRI</span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>報告警告，到<span lang='EN-US'>2025</span>年，較嚴格的政府氣候法規恐使若干行業的公司價值縮水。<span lang='EN-US'>(</span>圖<span lang='EN-US'>: pixabay)</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>投資者團體「責任投資原則」<span lang='EN-US'>(Principles of Responsible Investing, PRI)</span>在報告中警告，到<span lang='EN-US'>2025</span>年，較嚴格的政府氣候法規恐使若干行業的公司價值縮水多達<span lang='EN-US'>2.3</span>兆美元，受影響廠商包括化石燃料生產、農業和汽車製造業者。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>路透社報導，隨著各國爭相履行義務，以達成<span lang='EN-US'>2015</span>年巴黎氣候協定限制全球暖化的目標，未來幾年可望加速落實相關法規，降低碳排放。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>聯合國支持的「責任投資原則」發布報告說，任何突然的政策轉變都可能嚴重破壞當前的投資策略。這個團體代表的投資者管理<span lang='EN-US'>86</span>兆美元資產。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>「責任投資原則」執行長雷諾茲<span lang='EN-US'>(Fiona Reynolds)</span>說：「隨著氣候變遷事實的發展，社會壓力與日俱增，低碳解決方案變得愈來愈便宜，各國政府不大可能在未被迫早日採取有力行動的情況下，放任各界忽視氣溫節節高升。」</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>「這對資產和整個系統構成了巨大威脅。」</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>報告說，首當其衝的是化石燃料行業，可能損失當前價值的三分之一。化石燃料約占全球溫室氣體排放量的三分之二。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>根據報告，燃煤公司價值可能暴跌高達<span lang='EN-US'>44%</span>，全球規模最大的石油和天然氣公司則可能失去多達<span lang='EN-US'>31%</span>現有市占率。這份報告預測石油需求將在<span lang='EN-US'>2027</span>年前後達到巔峰。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>分析顯示，在最極端的情況下，諸如<span lang='EN-US'>iShares MSCI ACWI ETF</span>等指數型基金的價值可能損失多達<span lang='EN-US'>4.5%</span>或<span lang='EN-US'>2.3</span>兆美元。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>然而，這樣的轉變也可能催生贏家。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>報告說，大力投資電動車的汽車製造商和推動低碳電力的電力公司，公司價值可能增加一倍以上。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2044264</span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2019-12-10","clk_count":"113"}},"__N_SSG":true}